    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. The CFD model demonstrates adequate predictive accuracy for hemolysis index across the CPB operating envelope. The grid independence study, solver verification, and experimental validation collectively support the claim that the model can identify worst-case hemolysis operating conditions. Six factors were not assessed, which is acceptable at MRL 2 for a Class II device with medium model influence. The overall credibility evidence package supports acceptance of the model for the stated COU.",
